column3:
Hiroyuki Endo (1), Chisa Hotta (1), Akira Shimizu (1 and 2) ((1)
  Department of Basic Science, The University of Tokyo, (2) Komaba Institute
  for Science, The University of Tokyo)

column11:
  We prove that the spectrum of the discrete Schr\"odinger operator on
$\ell^2(Z^2)$, $(\psi_{n,m})\mapsto -(\psi_{n+1,m} +\psi_{n-1,m} +\psi_{n,m+1}
+\psi_{n,m-1})+V_n\psi_{n,m}$ is absolutely continuous.
